chapters.title: Chapter 5:  The Forging of a Hammer
chapters.info:
Breane Taborwin,
      p. 185 (212)—Woman
      from Cairhien who is Lamgwin's love interest.
      She is now one of Faile's personal maids along with
      “Maighdin.” and
      Lini.  She hates Berelain.
      See also
      Dorn, Lamgwin;
      Taborwin, Dobraine.
